10. Governance & Safety

The Silence Machine governance plan already forbids:
	•	covert channels
	•	hidden instructions
	•	unsafe signaling
	•	unauthorized remote influence

Apocopated symmetry is safe because:
	•	The omitted word is non-functional (poetic, narrative).
	•	Reconstruction is local, interpretive, and non-actionable.
	•	It is used for meaning, not for hidden control.
	•	All experiments must occur in an air-gapped sandbox per Arctic governance checklist.

Thus it is allowed under PantheonOS doctrine.

